title: 8-9am- New Music & Nose Picking

description: We are dressing up in studio for Halloween, Sarah wants to decorate, A special edition of the Beetle’s Revolver out now, a best of album is out for the Foo Fighters, Christmas music is in full force, Pentatonix has a new Christmas album, Some rocking country from Laney Wilson, we check out a band for Vinnie, Billie Eilish’s brother was badly injured in a bike accident, the Ravens beat the Bucs, the World Series starts tonight, Nancy Pelosi’s husband was violently assaulted in their home, a study on nose picking found we are no the only ones who do it, a group in Belgium wants to make rescue rats, eating sand to lose weight, the top things that can scare someone off an a first date, some fast facts, and Vinnie reads your texts!
